# VHS tape for the README demo GIF.
# Regenerate with: vhs demo.tape   (run from inside assets/demo/applying-nasa-dod-coding-standards/)
# Requires: https://github.com/charmbracelet/vhs (and ffmpeg + ttyd)

Output demo.gif

Set Shell "bash"
Set FontSize 16
Set Width 1000
Set Height 560
Set Padding 20
Set Theme "Dracula"
Set TypingSpeed 60ms

Hide
Type "clear && bash repl.sh"
Enter
Sleep 500ms
Show

Type "implement a rate limiter for the API gateway"
Sleep 600ms
Enter

Sleep 11s
